                    345
                    !
                    
                      
      result <- adtte_joined[subset_rows, , drop = FALSE]

                    		
                  

                  

                    346
                    !
                    
                      
      droplevels(result)

                    		
                  

                  

                    347
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    348
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    349
                    !
                    
                      
    binned_adtte_subset <- reactive({

                    		
                  

                  

                    350
                    !
                    
                      
      gene_col <- gene_col()

                    		
                  

                  

                    351
                    !
                    
                      
      probs <- probs()

                    		
                  

                  

                    352
                    !
                    
                      
      adtte_subset <- adtte_subset()

                    		
                  

                  

                    353
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    354
                    !
                    
                      
      result <- tryCatch(

                    		
                  

                  

                    355
                    !
                    
                      
        expr = {

                    		
                  

                  

                    356
                    !
                    
                      
          dplyr::mutate(

                    		
                  

                  

                    357
                    !
                    
                      
            adtte_subset,

                    		
                  

                  

                    358
                    !
                    
                      
            gene_factor = tern::cut_quantile_bins(

                    		
                  

                  

                    359
                    !
                    
                      
              adtte_subset[, gene_col],

                    		
                  

                  

                    360
                    !
                    
                      
              probs = probs

                    		
                  

                  

                    361
                    
                    
                      
            )

                    		
                  

                  

                    362
                    
                    
                      
          )

                    		
                  

                  

                    363
                    
                    
                      
        },

                    		
                  

                  

                    364
                    !
                    
                      
        error = function(e) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    365
                    !
                    
                      
          if (grepl("Contains duplicated values", e)) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    366
                    !
                    
                      
            validate(paste(

                    		
                  

                  

                    367
                    !
                    
                      
              "please adjust filters or select (slightly) different quantiles",

                    		
                  

                  

                    368
                    !
                    
                      
              "to avoid duplicate quantiles"

                    		
                  

                  

                    369
                    
                    
                      
            ))

                    		
                  

                  

                    370
                    
                    
                      
          } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    371
                    !
                    
                      
            stop(e)

                    		
                  

                  

                    372
                    
                    
                      
          }

                    		
                  

                  

                    373
                    
                    
                      
        }

                    		
                  

                  

                    374
                    
                    
                      
      )

                    		
                  

                  

                    375
                    !
                    
                      
      result

                    		
                  

                  

                    376
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    377
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    378
                    !
                    
                      
    time_unit <- reactive({

                    		
                  

                  

                    379
                    !
                    
                      
      adtte_subset <- adtte_subset()

                    		
                  

                  

                    380
                    !
                    
                      
      result <- unique(as.character(adtte_subset[[adtte_vars$avalu]]))

                    		
                  

                  

                    381
                    !
                    
                      
      assert_string(result)

                    		
                  

                  

                    382
                    !
                    
                      
      result

                    		
                  

                  

                    383
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    384
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    385
                    !
                    
                      
    list(

                    		
                  

                  

                    386
                    !
                    
                      
      binned_adtte_subset = binned_adtte_subset,

                    		
                  

                  

                    387
                    !
                    
                      
      gene_col = gene_col,

                    		
                  

                  

                    388
                    !
                    
                      
      gene_factor = "gene_factor",

                    		
                  

                  

                    389
                    !
                    
                      
      time_unit = time_unit

                    		
                  

                  

                    390
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    391
                    
                    
                      
  })

                    		
                  

                  

                    392
                    
                    
                      
}

tm_g_scatterplot <- function(label,

                    		
                  

                  

                    30
                    
                    
                      
                             mae_name,

                    		
                  

                  

                    31

                    35

                    40

                    41
                    !
                    
                      
  message("Initializing tm_g_scatterplot")

                    		
                  

                  

                    42

  assert_string(label)

                    		
                  

                  

                    43

  assert_string(mae_name)

                    		
                  

                  

                    44

  assert_character(exclude_assays, any.missing = FALSE)

                    		
                  

                  

                    45

                    46

                    47

  assert_tag(post_output, null.ok = TRUE)

                    50
                    !
                    
                      
    label = label,

    server = srv_g_scatterplot,

                    !
                    
                      
    server_args = list(

                    		
                  

                  

                    53
                    !
                    
                      
      mae_name = mae_name,

                    		
                  

                  

                    54
                    !
                    
                      
      summary_funs = summary_funs,

                    		
                  

                  

                    55
                    !
                    
                      
      exclude_assays = exclude_assays,

                    		
                  

                  

                    56
                    !
                    
                      
      .test = .test

                    		
                  

                  

                    57
                    
                    
                      
    ),

                    		
                  

                  

                    58

    ui = ui_g_scatterplot,

                    		
                  

                  

                    59
                    !
                    
                      
    ui_args = list(

                    		
                  

                  

                    60
                    !
                    
                      
      mae_name = mae_name,

                    		
                  

                  

                    61
                    !
                    
                      
      summary_funs = summary_funs,

                    		
                  

                  

                    62
                    !
                    
                      
      pre_output = pre_output,

                    		
                  

                  

                    63
                    !
                    
                      
      post_output = post_output,

                    		
                  

                  

                    64
                    !
                    
                      
      .test = .test

                    		
                  

                  

                    65
                    
                    
                      
    ),

#' @describeIn tm_g_volcanoplot sets up the server with reactive graph.

                    		
                  

                  

                    110
                    
                    
                      
#' @inheritParams module_arguments

                    		
                  

                  

                    111
                    
                    
                      
#' @export

                    		
                  

                  

                    112
                    
                    
                      
srv_g_volcanoplot <- function(id,

                    		
                  

                  

                    113
                    
                    
                      
                              data,

                    		
                  

                  

                    114
                    
                    
                      
                              filter_panel_api,

                    		
                  

                  

                    115
                    
                    
                      
                              reporter,

                    		
                  

                  

                    116
                    
                    
                      
                              mae_name,

                    		
                  

                  

                    117
                    
                    
                      
                              exclude_assays,

                    		
                  

                  

                    118
                    
                    
                      
                              .test = FALSE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    119
                    !
                    
                      
  with_reporter <- !missing(reporter) && inherits(reporter, "Reporter")

                    		
                  

                  

                    120
                    !
                    
                      
  assert_class(filter_panel_api, "FilterPanelAPI")

                    		
                  

                  

                    121
                    !
                    
                      
  checkmate::assert_class(data, "reactive")

                    		
                  

                  

                    122
                    !
                    
                      
  checkmate::assert_class(shiny::isolate(data()), "teal_data")

                    		
                  

                  

                    123
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    124
                    !
                    
                      
  moduleServer(id, function(input, output, session) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    125
                    !
                    
                      
    teal.logger::log_shiny_input_changes(input, namespace = "teal.modules.hermes")

                    		
                  

                  

                    126
                    !
                    
                      
    output$experiment_ui <- renderUI({

                    		
                  

                  

                    127
                    !
                    
                      
      experimentSpecInput(session$ns("experiment"), data, mae_name)

                    		
                  

                  

                    128
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    129
                    !
                    
                      
    experiment_data <- experimentSpecServer(

                    		
                  

                  

                    130
                    !
                    
                      
      "experiment",

                    		
                  

                  

                    131
                    !
                    
                      
      data = data,

                    		
                  

                  

                    132
                    !
                    
                      
      mae_name = mae_name

                    		
                  

                  

                    133
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    !
                    
                      
    assay <- assaySpecServer(

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    !
                    
                      
      "assay",

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    !
                    
                      
      assays = experiment_data$assays,

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    !
                    
                      
      exclude_assays = exclude_assays

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    !
                    
                      
    compare_group <- sampleVarSpecServer(

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    !
                    
                      
      "compare_group",

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    !
                    
                      
      experiment_name = experiment_data$name,

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    !
                    
                      
      original_data = experiment_data$data,

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    !
                    
                      
      num_levels = 2L,

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    !
                    
                      
      label_modal_title = "Please click to group into exactly 2 levels, first level is reference"

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    
                    
                      
    # When the filtered data set or the chosen experiment changes, update

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    
                    
                      
    # the differential expression results.

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    !
                    
                      
    diff_expr <- reactive({

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    !
                    
                      
      object <- compare_group$experiment_data()

                    		
                  

                  

                    151
                    !
                    
                      
      compare_group <- compare_group$sample_var()

                    		
                  

                  

                    152
                    !
                    
                      
      method <- input$method

                    		
                  

                  

                    153
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    154
                    !
                    
                      
      req(

                    		
                  

                  

                    155
                    !
                    
                      
        object,

                    		
                  

                  

                    156
                    !
                    
                      
        method

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    
                    
                      
      )

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    !
                    
                      
      validate(need(

                    		
                  

                  

                    159
                    !
                    
                      
        !is.null(compare_group),

                    		
                  

                  

                    160
                    !
                    
                      
        "Please select a group variable"

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    
                    
                      
      ))

                    		
                  

                  

                    162
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    163
                    !
                    
                      
      hermes::diff_expression(

                    		
                  

                  

                    164
                    !
                    
                      
        object,

                    		
                  

                  

                    165
                    !
                    
                      
        group = compare_group,

                    		
                  

                  

                    166
                    !
                    
                      
        method = method

                    		
                  

                  

                    167
                    
                    
                      
      )

                    		
                  

                  

                    168
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    169
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    170
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_r <- reactive({

                    		
                  

                  

                    171
                    !
                    
                      
      diff_expr_result <- diff_expr()

                    		
                  

                  

                    172
                    !
                    
                      
      log2_fc_thresh <- input$log2_fc_thresh

                    		
                  

                  

                    173
                    !
                    
                      
      adj_p_val_thresh <- input$adj_p_val_thresh

                    		
                  

                  

                    174
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    175
                    !
                    
                      
      req(

                    		
                  

                  

                    176
                    !
                    
                      
        log2_fc_thresh,

                    		
                  

                  

                    177
                    !
                    
                      
        adj_p_val_thresh

                    		
                  

                  

                    178
                    
                    
                      
      )

                    		
                  

                  

                    179
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    180
                    !
                    
                      
      hermes::autoplot(

                    		
                  

                  

                    181
                    !
                    
                      
        diff_expr_result,

                    		
                  

                  

                    182
                    !
                    
                      
        adj_p_val_thresh = adj_p_val_thresh,

                    		
                  

                  

                    183
                    !
                    
                      
        log2_fc_thresh = log2_fc_thresh

                    		
                  

                  

                    184
                    
                    
                      
      )

                    		
                  

                  

                    185
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    186
                    !
                    
                      
    output$plot <- renderPlot(plot_r())

                    		
                  

                  

                    187
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    188
                    !
                    
                      
    pws_p <- teal.widgets::plot_with_settings_srv(

                    		
                  

                  

                    189
                    !
                    
                      
      id = "plot",

                    		
                  

                  

                    190
                    !
                    
                      
      plot_r = plot_r

                    		
                  

                  

                    191
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    192
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    193
                    
                    
                      
    # Display top genes if switched on.

                    		
                  

                  

                    194
                    !
                    
                      
    show_top_gene_diffexpr <- reactive({

                    		
                  

                  

                    195
                    !
                    
                      
      if (input$show_top_gene) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    196
                    !
                    
                      
        result <- diff_expr()

                    		
                  

                  

                    197
                    !
                    
                      
        with(

                    		
                  

                  

                    198
                    !
                    
                      
          result,

                    		
                  

                  

                    199
                    !
                    
                      
          data.frame(

                    		
                  

                  

                    200
                    !
                    
                      
            log2_fc = round(log2_fc, 2),

                    		
                  

                  

                    201
                    !
                    
                      
            stat = round(stat, 2),

                    		
                  

                  

                    202
                    !
                    
                      
            p_val = format.pval(p_val),

                    		
                  

                  

                    203
                    !
                    
                      
            adj_p_val = format.pval(adj_p_val),

                    		
                  

                  

                    204
                    !
                    
                      
            row.names = rownames(result)

                    		
                  

                  

                    205
                    
                    
                      
          )

                    		
                  

                  

                    206
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    207
                    
                    
                      
      } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    208
                    !
                    
                      
        NULL

                    		
                  

                  

                    209
                    
                    
                      
      }

                    		
                  

                  

                    210
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    211
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    212
                    !
                    
                      
    output$table <- DT::renderDT({

                    		
                  

                  

                    213
                    !
                    
                      
      DT::datatable(

                    		
                  

                  

                    214
                    !
                    
                      
        show_top_gene_diffexpr(),

                    		
                  

                  

                    215
                    !
                    
                      
        rownames = TRUE,

                    		
                  

                  

                    216
                    !
                    
                      
        options = list(scrollX = TRUE, pageLength = 30, lengthMenu = c(5, 15, 30, 100)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    217
                    !
                    
                      
        caption = "Top Differentiated Genes"

                    		
                  

                  

                    218
                    
                    
                      
      )

                    		
                  

                  

                    219
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    220
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    221
                    !
                    
                      
    if (.test) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    222
                    !
                    
                      
      output$test <- renderPrint(layer_data(plot_r()))

                    		
                  

                  

                    223
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    224
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    225
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    226
                    
                    
                      
    ### REPORTER

                    		
                  

                  

                    227
                    !
                    
                      
    if (with_reporter) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    228
                    !
                    
                      
      card_fun <- function(comment, label) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    229
                    !
                    
                      
        card <- report_card_template(

                    		
                  

                  

                    230
                    !
                    
                      
          title = "Volcano Plot",

                    		
                  

                  

                    231
                    !
                    
                      
          label = label,

                    		
                  

                  

                    232
                    !
                    
                      
          with_filter = TRUE,

                    		
                  

                  

                    233
                    !
                    
                      
          filter_panel_api = filter_panel_api

                    		
                  

                  

                    234
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    235
                    !
                    
                      
        card$append_text("Selected Options", "header3")

                    		
                  

                  

                    236
                    !
                    
                      
        encodings_list <- list(

                    		
                  

                  

                    237
                    !
                    
                      
          "Experiment:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    238
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`experiment-name`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    239
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nAssay:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    240
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`assay-name`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    241
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nCompare Groups:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    242
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`compare_group-sample_var`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    243
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nShow Top Differentiated Genes:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    244
                    !
                    
                      
          input$show_top_gene,

                    		
                  

                  

                    245
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nMethod:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    246
                    !
                    
                      
          input$method,

                    		
                  

                  

                    247
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nLog2fold Change Threshold:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    248
                    !
                    
                      
          input$log2_fc_thresh,

                    		
                  

                  

                    249
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nAdjusted P-value Threshold:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    250
                    !
                    
                      
          input$adj_p_val_thresh

                    		
                  

                  

                    251
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    252
                    !
                    
                      
        null_encodings_indices <- which(sapply(encodings_list, function(x) is.null(x) || x == ""))

                    		
                  

                  

                    253
                    !
                    
                      
        final_encodings <- if (length(null_encodings_indices) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    254
                    !
                    
                      
          null_encodings_indices_1 <- c(null_encodings_indices, null_encodings_indices - 1)

                    		
                  

                  

                    255
                    !
                    
                      
          paste(encodings_list[-null_encodings_indices_1], collapse = " ")

                    		
                  

                  

                    256
                    
                    
                      
        } else {

                    		
                  

                  

                    257
                    !
                    
                      
          paste(encodings_list, collapse = " ")

        card$append_text("Plot", "header3")

                    !

        card

                    		
                  

                  

                    272
                    
                    
                      
      }

                    !
                    
                      
      teal.reporter::simple_reporter_srv("simple_reporter", reporter = reporter, card_fun = card_fun)

    }

#' Teal Module for RNA-seq Boxplot

                    		
                  

                  

                    2
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    3
                    
                    
                      
#' @description `r lifecycle::badge("experimental")`

                    		
                  

                  

                    4
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    5
                    
                    
                      
#' This module provides an interactive boxplot for RNA-seq gene expression

                    		
                  

                  

                    6
                    
                    
                      
#' analysis.

                    		
                  

                  

                    7
                    
                    
                      
#'

                    		
                  

                  

                    8
                    
                    
                      
#' @inheritParams module_arguments

                    		
                  

                  

                    9
                    
                    
                      
#' @inheritParams teal::module

                    		
                  

                  

                    10

#' @describeIn tm_g_boxplot sets up the server with reactive graph.

                    		
                  

                  

                    131

srv_g_boxplot <- function(id,

                    		
                  

                  

                    134
                    
                    
                      
                          data,

                    		
                  

                  

                    135
                    
                    
                      
                          filter_panel_api,

                    		
                  

                  

                    136
                    
                    
                      
                          reporter,

                    		
                  

                  

                    137
                    
                    
                      
                          mae_name,

                    		
                  

                  

                    138
                    
                    
                      
                          exclude_assays,

                    		
                  

                  

                    139
                    
                    
                      
                          summary_funs,

                    		
                  

                  

                    140
                    
                    
                      
                          .test = FALSE) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    141
                    !
                    
                      
  with_reporter <- !missing(reporter) && inherits(reporter, "Reporter")

                    		
                  

                  

                    142
                    !
                    
                      
  assert_class(filter_panel_api, "FilterPanelAPI")

                    		
                  

                  

                    143
                    !
                    
                      
  checkmate::assert_class(data, "reactive")

                    		
                  

                  

                    144
                    !
                    
                      
  checkmate::assert_class(shiny::isolate(data()), "teal_data")

                    		
                  

                  

                    145
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    146
                    !
                    
                      
  moduleServer(id, function(input, output, session) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    147
                    !
                    
                      
    teal.logger::log_shiny_input_changes(input, namespace = "teal.modules.hermes")

                    		
                  

                  

                    148
                    !
                    
                      
    output$experiment_ui <- renderUI({

                    		
                  

                  

                    149
                    !
                    
                      
      experimentSpecInput(session$ns("experiment"), data, mae_name)

                    		
                  

                  

                    150
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    151
                    !
                    
                      
    experiment <- experimentSpecServer(

                    		
                  

                  

                    152
                    !
                    
                      
      "experiment",

                    		
                  

                  

                    153
                    !
                    
                      
      data = data,

                    		
                  

                  

                    154
                    !
                    
                      
      filter_panel_api = filter_panel_api,

                    		
                  

                  

                    155
                    !
                    
                      
      mae_name = mae_name

                    		
                  

                  

                    156
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    157
                    !
                    
                      
    assay <- assaySpecServer(

                    		
                  

                  

                    158
                    !
                    
                      
      "assay",

                    		
                  

                  

                    159
                    !
                    
                      
      assays = experiment$assays,

                    		
                  

                  

                    160
                    !
                    
                      
      exclude_assays = exclude_assays

                    		
                  

                  

                    161
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    162
                    !
                    
                      
    multi <- multiSampleVarSpecServer(

                    		
                  

                  

                    163
                    !
                    
                      
      inputIds = c("strat", "color", "facet"),

                    		
                  

                  

                    164
                    !
                    
                      
      experiment_name = experiment$name,

                    		
                  

                  

                    165
                    !
                    
                      
      original_data = experiment$data

                    		
                  

                  

                    166
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    167
                    !
                    
                      
    genes <- geneSpecServer(

                    		
                  

                  

                    168
                    !
                    
                      
      "genes",

                    		
                  

                  

                    169
                    !
                    
                      
      funs = summary_funs,

                    		
                  

                  

                    170
                    !
                    
                      
      gene_choices = experiment$genes

                    		
                  

                  

                    171
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    172
                    !
                    
                      
    plot_r <- reactive({

                    		
                  

                  

                    173
                    
                    
                      
      # Resolve all reactivity.

                    		
                  

                  

                    174
                    !
                    
                      
      experiment_data <- multi$experiment_data()

                    		
                  

                  

                    175
                    !
                    
                      
      strat <- multi$vars$strat()

                    		
                  

                  

                    176
                    !
                    
                      
      genes <- genes()

                    		
                  

                  

                    177
                    !
                    
                      
      facet <- multi$vars$facet()

                    		
                  

                  

                    178
                    !
                    
                      
      color <- multi$vars$color()

                    		
                  

                  

                    179
                    !
                    
                      
      assay <- assay()

                    		
                  

                  

                    180
                    !
                    
                      
      jitter <- input$jitter

                    		
                  

                  

                    181
                    !
                    
                      
      violin <- input$violin

                    		
                  

                  

                    182
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    183
                    !
                    
                      
      req(

                    		
                  

                  

                    184
                    !
                    
                      
        assay,

                    		
                  

                  

                    185
                    
                    
                      
        # Note: The following statements are important to make sure the UI inputs have been updated.

                    		
                  

                  

                    186
                    !
                    
                      
        isTRUE(assay %in% SummarizedExperiment::assayNames(experiment_data)),

                    		
                  

                  

                    187
                    !
                    
                      
        is.null(facet) || isTRUE(facet %in% names(SummarizedExperiment::colData(experiment_data))),

                    		
                  

                  

                    188
                    !
                    
                      
        is.null(color) || isTRUE(color %in% names(SummarizedExperiment::colData(experiment_data))),

                    		
                  

                  

                    189
                    !
                    
                      
        is.null(strat) || isTRUE(strat %in% names(SummarizedExperiment::colData(experiment_data))),

                    		
                  

                  

                    190
                    !
                    
                      
        cancelOutput = FALSE

                    		
                  

                  

                    191
                    
                    
                      
      )

                    		
                  

                  

                    192
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    193
                    !
                    
                      
      validate_gene_spec(genes, rownames(experiment_data))

                    		
                  

                  

                    194
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    195
                    !
                    
                      
      hermes::draw_boxplot(

                    		
                  

                  

                    196
                    !
                    
                      
        object = experiment_data,

                    		
                  

                  

                    197
                    !
                    
                      
        assay_name = assay,

                    		
                  

                  

                    198
                    !
                    
                      
        genes = genes,

                    		
                  

                  

                    199
                    !
                    
                      
        x_var = strat,

                    		
                  

                  

                    200
                    !
                    
                      
        facet_var = facet,

                    		
                  

                  

                    201
                    !
                    
                      
        color_var = color,

                    		
                  

                  

                    202
                    !
                    
                      
        jitter = jitter,

                    		
                  

                  

                    203
                    !
                    
                      
        violin = violin

                    		
                  

                  

                    204
                    
                    
                      
      )

                    		
                  

                  

                    205
                    
                    
                      
    })

                    		
                  

                  

                    206
                    !
                    
                      
    output$plot <- renderPlot(plot_r())

                    		
                  

                  

                    207
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    208
                    !
                    
                      
    pws <- teal.widgets::plot_with_settings_srv(

                    		
                  

                  

                    209
                    !
                    
                      
      id = "plot",

                    		
                  

                  

                    210
                    !
                    
                      
      plot_r = plot_r

                    		
                  

                  

                    211
                    
                    
                      
    )

                    		
                  

                  

                    212
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    213
                    !
                    
                      
    if (.test) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    214
                    !
                    
                      
      table_r <- reactive({

                    		
                  

                  

                    215
                    !
                    
                      
        utils::str(layer_data(plot_r()))

                    		
                  

                  

                    216
                    
                    
                      
      })

                    		
                  

                  

                    217
                    !
                    
                      
      output$table <- renderPrint(table_r())

                    		
                  

                  

                    218
                    
                    
                      
    }

                    		
                  

                  

                    219
                    
                    
                      

                    		
                  

                  

                    220
                    
                    
                      
    ### REPORTER

                    		
                  

                  

                    221
                    !
                    
                      
    if (with_reporter) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    222
                    !
                    
                      
      card_fun <- function(comment, label) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    223
                    !
                    
                      
        card <- report_card_template(

                    		
                  

                  

                    224
                    !
                    
                      
          title = "Boxplot",

                    		
                  

                  

                    225
                    !
                    
                      
          label = label,

                    		
                  

                  

                    226
                    !
                    
                      
          with_filter = TRUE,

                    		
                  

                  

                    227
                    !
                    
                      
          filter_panel_api = filter_panel_api

                    		
                  

                  

                    228
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    229
                    !
                    
                      
        card$append_text("Selected Options", "header3")

                    		
                  

                  

                    230
                    !
                    
                      
        encodings_list <- list(

                    		
                  

                  

                    231
                    !
                    
                      
          "Experiment:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    232
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`experiment-name`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    233
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nAssay:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    234
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`assay-name`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    235
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nFacetting Variable:",

                    !
                    
                      
          input$`facet-sample_var`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    237
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nGenes Selected:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    238
                    !
                    
                      
          paste0(genes()$get_gene_labels(), collapse = ", "),

                    		
                  

                  

                    239
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nGene Summary:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    240
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`genes-fun_name`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    241
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nJitter:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    242
                    !
                    
                      
          input$jitter,

                    		
                  

                  

                    243
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nViolin:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    244
                    !
                    
                      
          input$violin,

                    		
                  

                  

                    245
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nOptional Stratifying Variable:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    246
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`strat-sample_var`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    247
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nOptional Color Variable:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    248
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`color-sample_var`,

                    		
                  

                  

                    249
                    !
                    
                      
          "\nOptional Facet Variable:",

                    		
                  

                  

                    250
                    !
                    
                      
          input$`facet-sample_var`

                    		
                  

                  

                    251
                    
                    
                      
        )

                    		
                  

                  

                    252
                    !
                    
                      
        null_encodings_indices <- which(sapply(encodings_list, function(x) is.null(x) || x == ""))

                    		
                  

                  

                    253
                    !
                    
                      
        final_encodings <- if (length(null_encodings_indices) > 0) {

                    		
                  

                  

                    254
                    !
                    
                      
          null_encodings_indices_1 <- c(null_encodings_indices, null_encodings_indices - 1)

                    !
                    
                      
          paste(encodings_list[-null_encodings_indices_1], collapse = " ")

        } else {

                    !
                    
                      
          paste(encodings_list, collapse = " ")

        card$append_plot(plot_r(), dim = pws$dim())

                    !
                    
                      
        if (!comment == "") {

                    !
